    {"type":"text","id":"loop_s4_h","x":1290,"y":1004,"width":320,"height":24,"text":"4. TOOLING (optional)","originalText":"4. TOOLING (optional)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#78350f","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":8052,"version":1,"versionNonce":8053,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"loop_s4_b","x":1290,"y":1036,"width":320,"height":146,"text":"If the rule can be mechanized,\nthe tooling agent adds:\n\n  · loader validator\n  · renderer guard\n  · CLI subcommand\n  · pak-compare rule\n\nso the next user never sees the\nsame mistake.","originalText":"If the rule can be mechanized,\nthe tooling agent adds:\n\n  · loader validator\n  · renderer guard\n  · CLI subcommand\n  · pak-compare rule\n\nso the next user never sees the\nsame mistake.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#78350f","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":8054,"version":1,"versionNonce":8055,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"loop_s5","x":1680,"y":990,"width":340,"height":200,"strokeColor":"#15803d","backgroundColor":"#bbf7d0","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":8060,"version":1,"versionNonce":8061,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","id":"loop_s5_h","x":1690,"y":1004,"width":320,"height":24,"text":"5. SHIPS WITH REPO","originalText":"5. SHIPS WITH REPO","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#14532d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":8062,"version":1,"versionNonce":8063,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"loop_s5_b","x":1690,"y":1036,"width":320,"height":146,"text":"Git commit · push · PR.\n\nNext clone, next session, next\nuser starts at the new baseline.\n\nThe framework is smarter on\nevery iteration without anyone\nholding state in their head.","originalText":"Git commit · push · PR.\n\nNext clone, next session, next\nuser starts at the new baseline.\n\nThe framework is smarter on\nevery iteration without anyone\nholding state in their head.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#14532d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":8064,"version":1,"versionNonce":8065,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"loop_s6","x":2080,"y":990,"width":640,"height":200,"strokeColor":"#7f1d1d","backgroundColor":"#fee2e2","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":3,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":8070,"version":1,"versionNonce":8071,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","id":"loop_s6_h","x":2090,"y":1004,"width":620,"height":24,"text":"TOOLSET GAP ESCAPE","originalText":"TOOLSET GAP ESCAPE","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#7f1d1d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":8072,"version":1,"versionNonce":8073,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"loop_s6_b","x":2090,"y":1036,"width":620,"height":146,"text":"When an author agent needs a capability the framework doesn't\nhave yet, it raises a TOOLSET GAP rather than silently\nworking around. The orchestrator chooses:\n\n  · PUNT to the user (trim the request)\n  · API-EXPLORER (we don't know the wire format)\n  · TOOLING (fix the loader / renderer / CLI)\n\nNever ignore a gap report. Never silently downgrade.","originalText":"When an author agent needs a capability the framework doesn't\nhave yet, it raises a TOOLSET GAP rather than silently\nworking around. The orchestrator chooses:\n\n  · PUNT to the user (trim the request)\n  · API-EXPLORER (we don't know the wire format)\n  · TOOLING (fix the loader / renderer / CLI)\n\nNever ignore a gap report. Never silently downgrade.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#7f1d1d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":8074,"version":1,"versionNonce":8075,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},

